  character: {fileID: 21300000, guid: b191762417f78494b84b1ac0497e90a0, type: 3}
  description: "You\u2019ve mastered the ancient art of making problems disappear\u2026
    unfortunately not in the right way. Things magically vanish into bags, corners,
    or \u201CI\u2019ll deal with it later.\u201D"
